data.description: Welcome to this stunning Waterfront Custom 4 sided brick Home!! This 6-bedroom, 4 bath, two-story lakefront home is in the desirable Windsor Estates. Built in 2016, this home boasts wonderful upgrades. Step inside to the long entry foyer, with an office and dining room to the left, and a bedroom and full bath to the right. The dream kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring an expansive island with a breakfast bar, beautiful cabinetry, stone counters, and a view to the family room. It is equipped with double wall ovens, a gas cooktop, vent hood, dishwasher, microwave, and a large custom pantry. The fireside family room is filled with natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. Upstairs, the Primary Suite offers tray ceilings, a large sitting room, and a luxurious bath with vaulted ceilings. The bath features two separate vanities, a soaking tub, a separate shower, and a spacious walk-in closet. The second floor also includes a convenient laundry room and four secondary bedrooms, each with vaulted ceilings. One of the bedrooms features a large walk-in closet and a private bathroom, while two other bedrooms share an adjoining bathroom with two separate vanities. The last bedroom also features a large walk-in closet. Enjoy the serene backyard and lake views from the sunroom, perfect for relaxation and entertaining. Whether enjoying a peaceful morning coffee or hosting soir es under the stars, this outdoor haven is sure to become your favorite retreat. The neighborhood amenities include a lake, playground, and swimming pool, providing endless opportunities for outdoor enjoyment. Imagine creating memories with loved ones in this beautifully designed space, where style meets functionality seamlessly. Located in McDonough, this home offers a perfect location with easy access to shopping, dining, and the interstate. With meticulous attention to detail and situated in the prestigious Windsor Estates, this home is an embodiment of elegance and comfort. Seize the opportunity to make this residence yours and experience the epitome of sophisticated living.
